    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I had the same issue. My problem was complicated object for serialization. One attribute of my object was <code>Map&lt;Object1, List&lt;Object2&gt;&gt;</code>. \nI changed this attribute like <code>List&lt;Object3&gt;</code> where <code>Object3</code> contains <code>Object1</code> and <code>Object2</code> and everything works fine.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
