    "question_id" : 22566433,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Add the HTTP header manager and add in it your API's header names and values.\ne.g. Content-type, Accept, etc. That will resolve your issue.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3723758,
      "reputation" : 13039,
      "user_id" : 3600553,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 71,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/beIr4.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Du-Lacoste",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/3600553/du-lacoste"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 7,
    "last_activity_date" : 1526473562,
    "creation_date" : 1526473562,
    "answer_id" : 50370921,
    "question_id" : 22566433,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you are using <code>AJAX</code> <code>jQuery</code> Request this is a must to apply. If not it will throw you <code>415</code> Error.</p>\n\n<pre><code>dataType: \"json\",\ncontentType:'application/json'\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 4180218,
      "reputation" : 115,
      "user_id" : 3425475,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 75,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/e0aeee334d3da937dbe181be7b7808f9?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "J&#233;j&#233;",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/3425475/j%c3%a9j%c3%a9"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 0,
    "last_activity_date" : 1527767064,
    "creation_date" : 1527767064,
    "answer_id" : 50623520,
    "question_id" : 22566433,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Add MappingJackson2HttpMessageConverter manually in configuration solved the problem for me :</p>\n\n<pre><code>@EnableWebMvc\n@Configuration\n@ComponentScan\npublic class RestConfiguration extends WebMvcConfigurerAdapter {\n\n    @Override\n    public void configureMessageConverters(List&lt;HttpMessageConverter&lt;?&gt;&gt; messageConverters) {\n        messageConverters.add(new MappingJackson2HttpMessageConverter());\n        super.configureMessageConverters(messageConverters);\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1258846,
      "reputation" : 10592,
      "user_id" : 1217713,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/4ppt6.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Nalan Madheswaran",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1217713/nalan-madheswaran"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 8,
    "last_activity_date" : 1555985984,
    "creation_date" : 1555985984,
    "answer_id" : 55803411,
    "question_id" : 22566433,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you get this in React RSAA middleware or similar,\nAdd the headers:</p>\n\n<pre><code>  method: 'POST',\n  headers: {\n    'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n  },\n  body: JSON.stringify(model),\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3549742,
      "reputation" : 5001,
