    "body" : "<p>I fixed this by updating the <code>Request</code> class that my Controller receives.</p>\n\n<p>I <strong>removed</strong> the following class level annotation from my <code>Request</code> class on my server side. After that my client <strong>didn't get 415 error.</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>import javax.xml.bind.annotation.XmlRootElement;\n@XmlRootElement\n</code></pre>\n"
