    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Incase if you are giving a post request through <code>Postman</code> then make sure you have choosed these 2 options</p>\n<p><strong>1.</strong> <strong>JSON (application/json)</strong> should be choosed\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/aDQFM.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/aDQFM.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>2. Content-Type</strong> - application/json</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/LRorI.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/LRorI.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
